          What We're <span class="gradient-text">Building</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="gradient-border bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 card-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan to-accent-cyan flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0">
